Here are 6 key reasons why the token holds promising potential.

💡Before delving deeper, a brief overview 

• Render Network is a decentralized GPU-based rendering service provider.

• Creators submit rendering tasks, and Node Operators provide their unused GPU resources to execute these tasks.

That's all you need to know. Simple, right?

1⃣ OTOY, GPU-Rendering

• Render Network's parent company OTOY
• OTOY partners with Apple, Google, Microsoft, HBO
• OctaneX on Apple's App Store

🔹Unlike many crypto products and services, the Render Network can address most of the market's demand through its relationship with OTOY/Octane.

2⃣ AI Boom is coming

• CAGR of 36.8% expected from '22-'32
• Global chatbot market to hit $5B in 2022
• Big Tech's AI race intensifies, raising H100 GPU prices by 30% YoY due to generative AI rivalry. 

🔹The rising cost will likely spur demand for affordable, decentralized GPU markets.

3⃣ Road to Deflation

• Total Supply - 530M + 107M
• Circulating Supply - 372M (69%)
• Render introduces Burn-and-Mint Equilibrium, minting 107M new tokens to incentivize stakeholders.

🔹This move aims to make $RNDR net deflationary with no maximum supply.

4⃣ Expansion into AI & ML

• Upcoming Opt-in feature for Node Operators
• Opt-in diversifies Nodes with AI/ML
• The API offers Node Operators an additional income source beyond just rendering for the Render Network.

🔹In this project, similar to DeFi's TVL, the number of Nodes drives the project's momentum.

5⃣ Competitive advantages

• Cost-effective : Compared to centralized infrastructure, Render Network is 2-10x cheaper.

• High-quality Rendering : Capture (Lightspace) + Render (Octane) + Stream (ORBX Media Player)

• High-speed computation : Reduces queue time + compute time ~90%.

🔹For example, Render Network completed a 76-frame render in 15 minutes for $2.13, while a MacBook Pro took 25 hours.

6⃣ Bullish Governance

• RNP-001 : Burn-Mint Equilibrium
• RNP-002 : Solana migration
• RNP-003 : Core team grants
• RNP-004 : Open compute client (https://t.co/8HzcEXbBLm)
• RNP-005 : Beam compute Client

🔹All of this information will be presented at the upcoming  in Oct.

💡 My Opinion

- Expect to see at least five AI infrastructure projects in the top 20 cryptocurrencies within the next two years. Render Network is likely to be among them.

Starting our series on the [2024 Crypto Watchlist], Render Network is the initial project.
